# Educational Use License

## Red Box RPG - Version 0.1.0

Copyright (c) 2026 Old School RPG Team

---

## Educational Purpose

This project is a fan-created recreation of the classic 1980s Dungeons & Dragons Basic Set (Red Box Edition) created for **educational purposes only**. It demonstrates:

- Classic tabletop RPG game mechanics
- React application architecture
- Browser-based game development
- State management patterns
- Turn-based combat systems
- Data persistence techniques

---

## Permitted Use

This software is freely available for:

✅ **Personal Use** - Play and enjoy the game for personal entertainment  
✅ **Educational Use** - Study the code to learn web development and game design  
✅ **Academic Use** - Use as reference material in courses or research  
✅ **Modification** - Fork and modify for your own learning projects  
✅ **Attribution** - Share with proper attribution to the original creators  

---

