## Intellectual Property

### Dungeons & Dragons

**Dungeons & Dragons**, **D&D**, and the **Red Box** are trademarks of **Wizards of the Coast LLC**.

This project is:
- NOT affiliated with Wizards of the Coast
- NOT endorsed by Wizards of the Coast  
- NOT an official D&D product
- A fan-created educational project

### Game Mechanics

Game mechanics and rules are based on the 1981 D&D Basic Set as published by TSR, Inc. Game mechanics themselves are not copyrightable under U.S. law, but specific expression of those rules is copyrighted by Wizards of the Coast.

This implementation:
- Uses publicly available game mechanics
- Does not reproduce copyrighted text verbatim
- Provides original implementations and descriptions
- Credits the original creators and publishers

